SELECT ROUND(((CAST(current_date_value AS numeric) - CAST(previous_date_value AS numeric)) / CAST(previous_date_value AS numeric)) * 100, 2) AS percentage_change
FROM
  (
    SELECT 
      (SELECT CAST(total_bytes AS numeric) FROM public.summary WHERE "date" = CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '2 day') AS current_date_value,
      (SELECT CAST(total_bytes AS numeric) FROM public.summary WHERE "date" = CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '3 day') AS previous_date_value
  ) AS subquery;
